params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"h_VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_KNAME\\" as \\"VEND_KNAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ZIP_CD\\" as \\"ZIP_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ADDRESS_1\\" as \\"ADDRESS_1\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ADDRESS_2\\" as \\"ADDRESS_2\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ADDRESS_K_1\\" as \\"ADDRESS_K_1\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ADDRESS_K_2\\" as \\"ADDRESS_K_2\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"TEL\\" as \\"TEL\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"FAX\\" as \\"FAX\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"EMAIL\\" as \\"EMAIL\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ORG\\" as \\"VEND_ORG\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_PERSON\\" as \\"VEND_PERSON\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"OWN_ORG_CD\\" as \\"OWN_ORG_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"OWN_ORG_NAME\\" as \\"OWN_ORG_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\" as \\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"OWN_PERSON_NAME\\" as \\"OWN_PERSON_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ROUND_TYP\\" as \\"ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"INSPC_ACPT_APP_TYP\\" as \\"INSPC_ACPT_APP_TYP\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"TAX_CD\\" as \\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\" as \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\" as \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ODR_FORM_FLG\\") as \\"ODR_FORM_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ODR_EDI_FLG\\") as \\"ODR_EDI_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ODR_FAX_FLG\\") as \\"ODR_FAX_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ODR_MAIL_FLG\\") as \\"ODR_MAIL_FLG\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_REM\\" as \\"VEND_REM\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"EXCH_TYP\\" as \\"EXCH_TYP\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"IMPORT_TRN_TYP\\" as \\"IMPORT_TRN_TYP\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\" as \\"CUR_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"CUR_CD\\" = M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\"(+)"

"insert into " +" M_VEND_CTRL(\\"VEND_CD\\", \\"VEND_NAME\\", \\"VEND_ANAME\\", \\"VEND_KNAME\\", \\"ZIP_CD\\", \\"ADDRESS_1\\", \\"ADDRESS_2\\", \\"ADDRESS_K_1\\", \\"ADDRESS_K_2\\", \\"TEL\\", \\"FAX\\", \\"EMAIL\\", \\"VEND_ORG\\", \\"VEND_PERSON\\", \\"OWN_ORG_CD\\", \\"OWN_ORG_NAME\\", \\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\", \\"OWN_PERSON_NAME\\", \\"ROUND_TYP\\", \\"INSPC_ACPT_APP_TYP\\", \\"TAX_CD\\", \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", \\"ODR_FORM_FLG\\", \\"ODR_EDI_FLG\\", \\"ODR_FAX_FLG\\", \\"ODR_MAIL_FLG\\", \\"VEND_REM\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"CUR_CD\\", \\"EXCH_TYP\\", \\"IMPORT_TRN_TYP\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?,( " +" select " +" COMPANY_CD " +" from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" where " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" ), ?, ?, ?)"

"update " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"set " +" \\"VEND_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_ANAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_KNAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"ZIP_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ADDRESS_1\\" = ?, " +" \\"ADDRESS_2\\" = ?, " +" \\"ADDRESS_K_1\\" = ?, " +" \\"ADDRESS_K_2\\" = ?, " +" \\"TEL\\" = ?, " +" \\"FAX\\" = ?, " +" \\"EMAIL\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_ORG\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_PERSON\\" = ?, " +" \\"OWN_ORG_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"OWN_ORG_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"OWN_PERSON_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"ROUND_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"INSPC_ACPT_APP_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"TAX_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"ODR_FORM_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"ODR_EDI_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"ODR_FAX_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"ODR_MAIL_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_REM\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUR_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"EXCH_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"IMPORT_TRN_TYP\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_PUCH_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_PUCH_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_PUCH_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PUCH_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC " +"where " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR " +"where " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"select " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_CD\\" as \\"TAX_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_TAX " +"where " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" SYS_HOME_CUR.\\"HOME_CUR_CD\\" as \\"HOME_CUR_CD\\" " +"from " +" SYS_HOME_CUR " +"where " +" SYS_HOME_CUR.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\" as \\"CUR_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\" as \\"OWN_PERSON_NAME\\" " +"from " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" AS \\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_PUCH_ODR_RTN_RSLT.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_PUCH_ODR_RTN_RSLT " +"WHERE " +" T_PUCH_ODR_RTN_RSLT.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_PUCH_ODR_RTN_RSLT.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" M.VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST M " +"WHERE " +" M.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M.VEND_CD = ?"
"select " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_TRANSPORT_STOCK " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND VEND_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND VEND_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" PAYEE_CD " +"FROM " +" T_DEBT_BALANCE " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND PAYEE_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_DEBT_BALANCE_D " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND(VEND_CD = ? " +" OR PAYEE_CD = ?)"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_DEBT_LEDGER_H " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND(VEND_CD = ? " +" OR PAYEE_CD = ?)"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_DEBT_LEDGER_H_TRN " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND(VEND_CD = ? " +" OR PAYEE_CD = ?)"
"SELECT " +" PAYEE_CD " +"FROM " +" T_PAYMENT " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND PAYEE_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" VEND_CD " +"FROM " +" T_PAYMENT_CALC " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND(VEND_CD = ? " +" OR PAYEE_CD = ?)"
"SELECT " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS.\\"INSTALL_FLG\\" AS \\"INSTALL_FLG\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS " +"WHERE " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS.\\"OPTION_ID\\" = ?"
